    <h2>Party Influence in French Electoral Manifestos</h2>
    <p>
      Analyzed French electoral manifestos to study whether political discourse is shaped more strongly
      by party ideology or by candidates’ socio-professional characteristics.
    </p>
    <p><strong>Tools:</strong> Python, NLP, topic modeling, regression</p>
    <p><a href="https://github.com/sarakpyny/french-political-text-analysis" target="_blank">View project</a></p>
